History: New right internal jugular central line placement.
Findings: Single AP view of the chest is provided. There has been interval placement of a right internal jugular line with tip residing in the distal SVC. There is no pneumothorax. Impression: Interval placement of right internal jugular line with tip in the distal SVC. No pneumothorax. Unchanged appearance of the lungs.
